What's strong:

Contextual referral timing — CTAs appear when users are primed (e.g., after learning about borrowing power, a mortgage broker CTA appears).
3 copy variants (soft/medium/direct) show sophisticated conversion thinking.
26 mapped touchpoints across stages and personas.
Question scripts make users feel prepared to speak to professionals, reducing friction.
