Content production is outstanding — the volume, quality, and structure of the written content is the best part of this project. Someone thought deeply about every stage.
Frontend is solid — React + TypeScript + shadcn is a good stack choice. Components are well-organized. Calculators work.
Planning documentation is thorough — specs, user flows, referral touchpoints, compliance templates. Shows professional product thinking.
