No backend infrastructure — forms don't submit, no database, no user accounts, no CMS. It's a frontend prototype.
No actual partner network — the entire business model depends on relationships that don't exist yet.
No analytics or tracking — no Google Analytics, no Hotjar, no funnel tracking. Flying blind.
